            <h2>Meet Avant</h2>
            <h4>Born June 2000</h4>
            <p>Avant is a very techsavvy young man who loves to play on his phone and with other gadgets. He loves video games and has mastered his favorite game, <em>Call of Duty</em>. Avant also enjoys board games and will persuade anyone to sit down with him and play a round of Monopoly.</p>
<p>Like most teenage boys, Avant is a die-hard sports fan. When it comes to playing a sport, he enjoys playing basketball with his friends or shooting hoops after school. When it comes to watching sports, Avant loves baseball and always cheers on the Cincinnati Reds whenever they play.</p>
<p>Also like most teenagers, Avant enjoys listening to music and watching tv. His favorite genre is rap and his favorite artist is Lil Wayne. Avant loves to laugh and enjoys any comedy shows and movies.</p>
<p>Avant has been described as a very quiet, responsible, sweet and respectful young man. He is great at helping with chores and always has his room clean. When the weather is nice, he enjoys being outside and helping with yard work. Avant says that he is most proud of how hard he works in school. He says that his favorite subject is science because he enjoys doing experiments and other hands-on activities.</p>
<p>Avant would do best in a family where he is the only child. He has expressed that he would like a family that enjoys doing activities and spending time together.</p>

